        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> I'm not sure what's the root cause, since from the code it already \"schedule\" the exit:\r\n\r\nOh... wait it's not, my bad\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/lua/fzf-lua/libuv.lua b/lua/fzf-lua/libuv.lua\r\nindex 4b6e7d8..28658e6 100644\r\n--- a/lua/fzf-lua/libuv.lua\r\n+++ b/lua/fzf-lua/libuv.lua\r\n@@ -547,9 +547,9 @@ M.spawn_stdio = function(opts)\r\n   local on_finish = function(code)\r\n     pipe_close(stdout)\r\n     pipe_close(stderr)\r\n-    if vim.in_fast_event() and fn_postprocess then\r\n+    if vim.in_fast_event() then\r\n       vim.schedule(function()\r\n-        fn_postprocess(opts)\r\n+        if fn_postprocess then fn_postprocess(opts) end\r\n         exit(code)\r\n       end)\r\n     else\r\n```",
            "created_at": "2026-05-21T02:54:37Z",
