        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "we generally want to fix crashes, that is never acceptable (except if a plugin uses FFI to reach into internals). https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/39783#issuecomment-4510216305",
            "created_at": "2026-05-21T16:13:09Z",
